#. ID 6, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (17,6)
msgid "聴きたい曲の番号を　入力してください。"
msgstr "Input the number of your desired song."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 1, Pos (6,7)
#. Contains choice at line 2 (3 options)
msgid "パンフレットが置いてある……"
msgstr "There are pamphlets here..."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (6,7)
#. Choice (3 options, embedded in a message)
msgid ""
"真・ゲルテナ展とは？\n"
"データの引き継ぎについて\n"
"黒のカギは？"
msgstr ""
"True Guertena Exhibit?\n"
"About data carry-over\n"
"What about the Black Key?"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 5, Pos (6,7)
msgid ""
"イヴが　今まで見てきた　美術品を\n"
"明かりの下で　鑑賞することが　できます。"
msgstr ""
"Here, Ib can appreciate all the artwork\n"
"she's seen thus far in a better light."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 8, Pos (6,7)
msgid ""
"ただし「イヴ自身」が　美術品の「正式名称」を\n"
"調べなければ　美術品は展示されません。\n"
"（読めない　タイトルは\n"
"ギャリーに読んでもらいましょう）"
msgstr ""
"However, the exhibition cannot\n"
"display any works which Ib herself\n"
"has not learned the official title of.\n"
"(Have Garry read those she can't read.)"

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 13, Pos (6,7)
msgid ""
"また　エンディングを１つ　見るごとに\n"
"真・ゲルテナ展のどこかに\n"
"キャラクターが　１人出現します。\n"
"最大で　４人まで増えます。"
msgstr ""
"For each new ending you see, an additional\n"
"character will appear in the true exhibition.\n"
"There are four characters in total."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 20, Pos (6,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"各エンディングを　見たあとに\n"
"そのデータのまま　新しくゲームをはじめると\n"
"今までに見た　美術品やエンディングの記録を\n"
"引きつぐことができます。"
msgstr ""
"By seeing an ending and then\n"
"starting anew with the same data,\n"
"your exhibits seen and endings\n"
"will be carried over."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 25, Pos (6,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"データを引きつぐと　以前調べた美術品や\n"
"見たエンディング数が　リセットされずに\n"
"再び　真・ゲルテナ展に来た時に\n"
"展示されたままに　なります。"
msgstr ""
"When data is carried over, your viewed\n"
"exhibits and endings will not be reset.\n"
"Upon future visits to the true exhibition,\n"
"they will remain on display."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 30, Pos (6,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"ただし　引きつぎデータは１つだけなので\n"
"他のセーブデータを　上書きしたり\n"
"NEW GAMEからはじめると　消えてしまいます。"
msgstr ""
"Be warned that this carry-over\n"
"data is tied to your save file.\n"
"If you choose \"New Game\" from the title\n"
"rather than continuing, it will be lost."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 36, Pos (6,7)
msgid ""
"黒のカギは　一度使用すれば\n"
"次からは　手に入れなくても\n"
"真・ゲルテナ展に　入る事ができます。"
msgstr ""
"The Black Key opens the true exhibition.\n"
"After the key has been used once,\n"
"you may visit the Guertena exhibition\n"
"without having to get the key again."

#. ID 7, Page 1, Line 40, Pos (6,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"ただし　真・ゲルテナ展は\n"
"イヴが　美術館を脱出した後にしか\n"
"入れないので　注意しましょう。"
msgstr ""
"Note, however, that the exhibition\n"
"can only be entered after endings\n"
"where Ib successfully escapes the gallery."

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 1, Pos (8,7)
msgid "「真・ゲルテナ展へ　ようこそ」"
msgstr "\"Welcome to the Guertena exhibition.\""

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (8,7)
msgid ""
"「ここでは　イヴ様が\n"
"　冒険の中で　見つけた\n"
"　美術品を　ご覧になれます」"
msgstr ""
"\"Here, you may view all the artworks\n"
"Lady Ib has seen on her adventure.\""

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 5, Pos (8,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"「ちなみに……タイトルのついた美術品は\n"
"　正式な作品名が　おわかりでなければ\n"
"　展示されないので　ご注意ください」"
msgstr ""
"\"However... If an artwork has a title,\n"
"and she doesn't know the proper name,\n"
"it won't go up on display.\""

#. ID 13, Page 1, Line 8, Pos (8,7)
#, fuzzy
msgid "「それでは　ごゆっくり　お楽しみくださいませ」"
msgstr "\"Now please, enjoy it at your leisure.\""

#. ID 14, Page 1, Line 1, Pos (0,8)
#. Contains choice at line 2 (2 options)
msgid "真・ゲルテナ展を出ますか？"
msgstr "Leave the true Guertena exhibit?"

#. ID 14, Page 1, Line 2, Pos (0,8)
#. Choice (2 options, embedded in a message)
msgid ""
"まだ出ない\n"
"出る"
msgstr ""
"Not yet\n"
"Leave"

